So the only thing to go off of is really just what Miyamoto said. And until the game is released and people ask more about the game.

topics.body:
"Ey, cap'! How did ya lose that eye?"
"Arr, it was a terrible fate, me lad. I had been sailing thee seas up North until..."
"Until what?"
"Until me ship and me crew were attacked by a bunch of filthy, good-for-nothing pirates!"
"Oh my!"
"Ay, it's true. We fought hardily and bravely. I too fought with me sword and peg leg."
"But what about the eye?"
"Oh that, I lost me eye after the battle."
"Ehh?"
"When we took their spoils and riches, we all had a roudy party, drinking rum and eating meat. But then, the ship hit a rock under the ocean and the entire ship rocked!"
"*gasp*"
"I was eating me soup when it happened. It startled me so much that I stabbed me self in the eye with the soup spoon!"
"..."
"What a terrible loss, it was..."
"... Okay... What about the ship?"
"Oh the ship's fine, lad. The only casualty was me eye."
